    public class LinkSetProperty<E extends EntityBean>
extends SetProperty<Link<E>>
    SetProperty with Set value containing Links that each point to an SimpleEntityBean. Unlike LinkListProperty the Links of an LinkSetProperty have no order and can not contain duplicates.
    Since:
    1.0.0
